720
00:56:50,639 --> 00:56:51,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ono je razvijelio, nisam znao.

721
00:56:51,940 --> 00:56:55,079
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, skoro sam zaboravio na ovu prvu encikliku.

722
00:56:55,079 --> 00:56:55,980
[SPEAKER_01] E, ali sad, čini mi se...

723
00:56:55,980 --> 00:56:56,840
[SPEAKER_01] I rjetko se spominja.

724
00:56:56,840 --> 00:56:58,780
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, gledaj sad, kad gledamo sve zajedno

725
00:56:58,780 --> 00:56:59,960
