726
00:56:59,960 --> 00:57:01,039
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, sabor je završio.

727
00:57:01,039 --> 00:57:02,840
[SPEAKER_00] Imamo, znači, presbitorom ovoga

728
00:57:02,840 --> 00:57:04,960
[SPEAKER_00] ordinis, imamo sacerdotalis celibatus.

729
00:57:04,960 --> 00:57:06,420
[SPEAKER_01] Koji reafirmi na celibatus.

730
00:57:06,420 --> 00:57:07,579
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je. I na neki način,

731
00:57:07,579 --> 00:57:08,579
