739
00:57:19,599 --> 00:57:21,119
[SPEAKER_00] koja je dovela do proizvodnje

740
00:57:21,119 --> 00:57:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] tog dokumenta.

741
00:57:22,000 --> 00:57:23,840
[SPEAKER_00] Međutim, nakon sabora,

742
00:57:23,840 --> 00:57:25,940
