748
00:57:32,780 --> 00:57:34,480
[SPEAKER_00] Sad, što se nakon toga događa?

749
00:57:34,480 --> 00:57:36,800
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, 65. odnosno 69. godine

750
00:57:36,800 --> 00:57:37,679
[SPEAKER_00] nakon sabora,

751
